{"tid":1447574,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"求下大家，可唔可以唔好走，唔好氣餒，一齊救手足？","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:02:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:06:58.000Z","uid":165425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7bf34b5c6ba26207c1f64270018d830aa0f02de7","tid":1447574,"uid":165425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:02:08.000Z","msg":"明明話大家一齊黎一齊走<br />\n有手足比人拉比人打，係應該救人，而唔係大難臨頭各自飛！<br />\n點解咁多條片得一個人係會救手足？<br />\n我都有發夢，我都知大家好驚，<br />\n但係我地係香港人黎架！我地係一條船上面架，再係咁樣條船就快沉架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我知大家仲諗緊點捉鬼，好嬲今日發生既事，<br />\n但係我好想大家記得，手足，係一定要救！盡力救得一個得一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />求下大家啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb362cd16ec6855cda14da04c65b35f8855fac8f","tid":1447574,"uid":165425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:03:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd2334a06b288a61392b491eca573f52cac3ed41","tid":1447574,"uid":165425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:04:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f5007dd84b00214cf6a0d121d640df47ea5c675","tid":1447574,"uid":165425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:06:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}